---
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
import Avatar from '../assets/avatar.webp';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Patrick Scheid - Senior Software Engineer"
    description="Senior Software Engineer at DeepL in Munich. Combining software engineering, data science, product management, and engineering leadership to build AI-powered products."
    pageClass="page-home"
>
    <section class="hero">
        <Image src={Avatar} alt="Patrick Scheid" class="hero-avatar" width={360} height={360} loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async"/>
        <h1>Hi, I'm Patrick!</h1>

        <p class="position">Senior Software Engineer @ DeepL</p>

        <p class="introduction">
            Senior software engineer with 9+ years of experience building and scaling backend systems, combined
            with 2+ years of engineering management. I bridge deep hands-on engineering in C#, Kotlin, and Go
            with a strong understanding of team dynamics, system design trade-offs, and cross-functional alignment.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="highlights">
        <h2>What I Bring</h2>
        <div class="highlights-grid">
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <span class="highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤖</span>
                <h3>AI / ML</h3>
                <p>Integrating LLM research into production editing tools serving 500k+ daily users at DeepL. Custom quality metrics, model evaluation, and end-to-end productionisation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <span class="highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</span>
                <h3>Backend Engineering</h3>
                <p>Building scalable systems in C#, Kotlin, and Go. Operated ~60 microservices on Kubernetes/AWS with Kafka, gRPC, and PostgreSQL.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <span class="highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</span>
                <h3>Data Engineering</h3>
                <p>End-to-end data pipelines, ETL design, and feature engineering. Built data analysis tools and validation pipelines for spectroscopy-based ML systems.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <span class="highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">📦</span>
                <h3>Product Ownership</h3>
                <p>Evolved a platform API into an API-as-a-Product with developer experience strategy, DX conversion funnel, and monetisation at Ryte.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <span class="highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">🧭</span>
                <h3>Engineering Management</h3>
                <p>Led teams of up to 8 engineers at DeepL. Hiring, mentoring, performance development, and guiding teams through reorgs and strategic shifts.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .hero {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2em 0 3em;
    }

    .hero-avatar {
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5em;
        display: block;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero .position {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin: 1em auto;
    }

    .hero .introduction {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 38rem;
    }

    .highlights {
        padding: 1em 0 3em;
    }

    .highlights h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

    .highlights-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .highlight-card {
        flex: 0 1 calc(33.333% - 1rem);
        background: var(--color-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5em;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .highlight-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    }

    .highlight-icon {
        font-size: 2rem;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .highlight-card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .highlight-card p {
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
        .hero-avatar {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
        }

        .highlight-card {
            flex: 0 1 calc(50% - 0.75rem);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .highlight-card {
            flex: 0 1 100%;
        }
    }
</style>
